description.en:
Info Notes Z-Notes post-its

These Z-Notes are certified with the Blue Angel label, the oldest eco-label in the world. All products are made of 100% recycled paper and produced in Germany with water-based and solvent-free adhesive. All products are available in an attractively designed packaging, manufactured from recycled materials. The dispenser box has an adhesive strip at the bottom so that the box remains stable.

Specifications:
Colour: yellow
Packaging colour: grey, blue
Gender: unisex
Material: paper (100% recycled)
Packaging material: cardboard
Dimensions post-its: 7.5 x 7.5 cm (L x W)
Dimensions packaging: 7.8 x 7.8 x 2.3 cm

Contents:
100 Post-its
